snippet.title: Wisdom Tree Collection (NES) Gameplay
snippet.description:
I received this all-in-one cartridge as a reward for Wisdom Tree's Kickstarter for "the Arkade" plug n play console. Interestingly, some of the game versions are actually not the latest version. I'm not familiar with the version differences, but I own version 1.2 of King of Kings, there's a 5.0 ROM online, and this collection as version 1.1. The game was produced by Niko Interactive which now owns Wisdom Tree apparently.
Anyway... the games included are... Sunday Funday, Spiritual Warfare, Joshua, Exodus, Bible Adventures, King of Kings: The Early Years, and Bible Buffet.
